Transaction list help legend: Transactions allow you to place new quote requests to your clients/ ecosystems/ Avenews-gt. You can also see all your transactions and make actions on them, easily!
Product list help legend: Here you can find all your products that you have uploaded, and create new ones!
Orders list help legend: Orders allow you to place new orders from your clients/ ecosystems/ Avenews-gt. You can also see all your orders and make actions on them, easily!
Invoice list help legend: Here you can see all your proforma invoices that have been sent to you!
